sf_uiModel.markdownText:
This is a markdown editor for creating text notes for your dashboards.
Enter your text or markdown on the left, and preview it on the right.
Here are some markdown examples:
#####_small headline italicized_ 1. ordered list 2. same ~~strike through~~ 
code segment
more code
this is a [link](https://signalfx.com) * bullet1 * bullet2 Click Create to save this text note to your dashboard.
